metadata.name: Video Call
metadata.description:
"Long distance
1500 miles
44 days to walk
Who cares? If you love me
As I love you
We’re not apart
Despite the miles
We are together
Together at heart
Distance matters to minds
But hearts don’t care"

In a long distance relationship, a girl took her phone to have a call with her boyfriend.

Poem quoted from "Miles away", uploaded on Momjunction.

Video Call - artwork hand drawn by Momi Momi.
